{
  "stem": "25589.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that was my dream that kept me happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all sorts of nice things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You kept yourself busy daydreaming about nice things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's what kept you going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The minute you start thinking about something bad, you get depressed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And depressed is very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If you can't get out-- with the four walls-- you're sitting between four walls-- it's bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I came out of the war-- and I'm getting ahead of me-- bad stomach.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all wound up with bad stomachs-- nervous stomachs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got-- I got a hiatus hernia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a hard word for me to say-- hiatus hernia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is that correct?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, well that's what I got.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got a bad back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we're thankful for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- I hope that answers your question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how we got through the days, because like I said, learning-- it would have been a good thing to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it worked out OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a businessman for 45 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I don't think I did so bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What for?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they were in anybody's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She could pick them up on her own name and from different people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- she had no problem with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That woman was fantastic with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got so hungry when-- I mean, what is two slices of bread a day?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The nicest part was when-- when-- when-- the-- the Red Cross dropped parcels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They dropped parcels.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each parcel had a white bread, which we hadn't seen in two years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a quarter of a pound of butter, if I remember correctly-- cheese, a little bit of cheese-- and it was, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
